Author: jakisaur
Text: chocolate is always last for me no matter when i eat it. so annoying bc it makes me feel like theres a ton of it left in my tum and its probs the most high calorie thing i ate.

Author: aceetone
Text: Yeah... I noticed this too. I think it's more due to your stomach physically mixing the food around using muscle contraction than it is food density making things sink.
